  ('optician-moex-01815', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一處方為+0.00DS/-1.25DC×180  ADD：+2.25 D，兩眼近用區均需 1.5ΔBI，若使用偏移的平頂子片 （flat-top segment）來產生近用稜鏡，則需將子片：', '["向上偏移", "向下偏移", "向外偏移", "向內偏移"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01816', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是雙側睫毛觸及鏡片的可能原因？', '["可調式鼻墊過於靠近鏡架前框", "可調式鼻墊彼此過於靠近", "前傾斜不足", "基弧過於扁平"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
